NBTObjectMapper<T extends Tag,O> - Interface in com.sudoplay.axion.mapper
The NBTObjectMapper interface allows mapper classes to be created to convert objects into tags.
NBTObjectMapperRegistry - Class in com.sudoplay.axion.mapper
The NBTObjectMapperRegistry is responsible for storing the object type to NBTObjectMapper relationship and providing a lookup method to retrieve the mapper from its type.
